    {
      "dot": "cyan",
      "title": "Frontend",
      "items": [
        "Vue Router exposes portal, college, university, and student screens",
        "Pinia and composables provide scope, refresh, scaling, and entrance logic",
        "Adapters convert API DTOs into view models before rendering"
      ]
    },
    {
      "dot": "emerald",
      "title": "Backend",
      "items": [
        "FastAPI initializes Tortoise during application lifespan",
        "Current implemented HTTP surface is GET /api/health",
        "Domain APIs under /api/v1 are represented in frontend contracts and pending server implementation"
      ]
    },
    {
      "dot": "amber",
      "title": "Data",
      "items": [
        "Excel files in Datas are imported through app/importers",
        "PostgreSQL stores the student_academic_records wide table",
        "app and backend currently keep separate Tortoise model definitions"
